WEBVTT

00:02:29.385 --> 00:02:31.977
the one I had to write for him,

00:02:32.001 --> 00:02:36.486
I discovered the power of an apology

00:02:36.510 --> 00:02:39.241
and how it actually might be
the way to move forward

00:02:39.265 --> 00:02:41.364
in the crisis we now face

00:02:41.388 --> 00:02:44.414
with men and all the women they abuse.

00:02:45.196 --> 00:02:48.966
Apology is a sacred commitment.

00:02:49.798 --> 00:02:52.061
It requires complete honesty.

00:02:52.719 --> 00:02:55.948
It demands deep
self-interrogation and time.

00:02:55.972 --> 00:02:57.671
It cannot be rushed.

00:02:58.052 --> 00:03:01.140
I discovered an apology has four steps,